{
  "stem": "22889.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father wrote to his uncle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is my grandfather brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They live in New York.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They still use the name Reibeisen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I changed my name, but I'll tell you after a while why.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father begged him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were pretty well off-- then already they were very well off, as a matter of fact-- not him, but his children-- very well off.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father begged him to save somebody from the farm-- my brother for instance.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, my father want to send my brother to the United States.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was already 16 years old, something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And no response-- very, very few.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why I don't have much contact with him, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How did you know that there was-- how did your father know that there was danger coming?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Were there any incidents in Nowy Targ?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we knew because they come from Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For instance, in 1933, we have a little pogrom in our town, which was nothing unusual, because some towns, they always have pogroms-- not always, but you heard about it-- I'm sure, here in the United States, too.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember this was during the summertime, because we were on vacation out of school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And me and my brother-- I was just a little fellow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I must have been about 8 years old-- something like that-- 7 years old, maybe.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were playing in the park.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The park was not too far from my home-- from my father's factory, actually.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In 1933, this was in July, I believe, that little program-- what started, the farmers start to complain to the government they didn't get enough pay for the product they brought to the-- to the market, and so forth on.",
      "word_count": 40
    }
  ],
